### Webhook PSP — wpłata (HMAC-SHA256 hex surowego body w nagłówku x-apexpay-signature; sekret = PSP_DEPOSIT_WEBHOOK_SECRET)
# Przykład podpisu (bash): BODY='{"pspRefId":"evt_1","userId":"USER_CUID","amount":5000,"currency":"PLN","status":"SUCCESS"}'; printf '%s' "$BODY" | openssl dgst -sha256 -hmac "TWÓJ_SEKRET" | awk '{print $2}'
POST {{rootUrl}}/internal/webhooks/psp-deposit
Content-Type: application/json
x-apexpay-signature: WKLEJ_HEX_64_ZNAKI

{
  "pspRefId": "evt_1",
  "userId": "USER_CUID",
  "amount": 5000,
  "currency": "PLN",
  "status": "SUCCESS"
}

### 0. Rejestracja (Zwróci 409 Conflict - to prawidłowe, konto już istnieje)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 1. Zaloguj się (Zwróci 200 OK)
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{email}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 2. Wpłać depozyt (100 PLN = 10000 groszy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/deposit
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "10000",
  "referenceId": "{{stripeRef}}"
}

### 3. Pobierz opłatę za turniej (10 PLN = 1000 groszy)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/charge
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "amount": "1000",
  "referenceId": "{{matchRef}}"
}

### 4. Utwórz nowy turniej (ApexPay)
POST {{baseUrl}}/tournaments
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "title": "Turniej Tekken 8 - Pro Series",
  "entryFeeCents": "5000",
  "maxPlayers": 128,
  "registrationEndsInHours": 48
}

### 4b. Lista turniejów (opcjonalnie ?limit=20&status=REGISTRATION)
# Odpowiedź: data.items[] — użyj pola tournamentId (CUID) do join.
GET {{baseUrl}}/tournaments
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 4c. Szczegół turnieju + drabinka (podmień {{tournamentId}})
# @tournamentId ustaw w sekcji 5 lub tutaj:
# @tournamentId = ...
GET {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{{tournamentId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Accept: application/json

### 5. Dołącz do turnieju (escrow wpisowego)
# tournamentId: z 4b → data.items[].tournamentId LUB z 4 (create) → data.tournamentId.
# Produkcja z tokenem z przeglądarki: join-tournament.private.http.example → join-tournament.private.http
@tournamentId = TUTAJ_WKLEJ_ID_TURNIEJU
POST {{baseUrl}}/tournaments/{{tournamentId}}/join
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Produkcja (apexpay.pl) — token z Local Storage: klucz apexpay_token
# Pełny opis: fund-wallet.http. Prywatne tokeny: fund-wallet.private.http (z .example).
# Test join + escrow: najpierw GET poniżej (lista turniejów) → tournamentId → join-tournament.private.http
@prodBase = https://apexpay.pl
@prodToken = WKLEJ_JWT_Z_LOGOWANIA
@adminUserId = WKLEJ_CUID_Z_auth_me

### 6a. Lista turniejów (prod) — data.items[].tournamentId do join
GET {{prodBase}}/api/tournaments
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Accept: application/json

GET {{prodBase}}/api/v1/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Accept: application/json

POST {{prodBase}}/api/v1/wallet/fund
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "targetUserId": "{{adminUserId}}",
  "amount": "100000"
}

### 7. SAFE TAXI — przejazd (prod: ustaw SAFE_TAXI_PLATFORM_USER_ID na serwerze)
# Utwórz przejazd jako pasażer (JWT), potem rozlicz jako kierowca (JWT kierowcy) lub ADMIN.
@stxDriverId = WKLEJ_CUID_KIEROWCY
@stxRideId = WKLEJ_PO_CREATE

POST {{prodBase}}/api/v1/safe-taxi/rides
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "driverUserId": "{{stxDriverId}}"
}

POST {{prodBase}}/api/v1/safe-taxi/rides/{{stxRideId}}/settle
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{prodToken}}
Accept: application/json

{
  "fareCents": "5000"
}

### Marketplace (ADMIN) — subkonto + charge split (localhost; podmień CUID i token ADMIN)
# @mktUserId = użytkownik z portfelem
# @mktConnId = z odpowiedzi POST .../connected-accounts
@mktUserId = WKLEJ_CUID
@mktConnId = WKLEJ_CONNECTED_ACCOUNT_ID

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/connected-accounts
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "userId": "{{mktUserId}}"
}

PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/v1/connected-accounts/{{mktConnId}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "ACTIVE"
}

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/charges
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Idempotency-Key: test-charge-001

{
  "debitUserId": "{{mktUserId}}",
  "amountCents": "1000",
  "splits": [
    { "connectedAccountId": "{{mktConnId}}", "amountCents": "1000" }
  ]
}